CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 19, 1957, pg. A2 reads: "Initiation - New members were initiated into the National Honor Society at Westinghouse High School. Seated, left to right: Judith Matthews, Dorothy Gloster, Toni Marsteller, Janice Finney, Susan Gray, Mildred Stewart, Diane DeHall.  Second row: John Haines Jr., Ruthann Colcombe, LaVerne Waddy, Fred Bilbrary, Dorothy Adams, Muriel Wilson and Fred DeReibertis.  Third row: Nick DiMomenico, Edwin Roberson, Godfrey Wills and John E. McCormick. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: National Honor Society members, seated from left: Judith Matthews, Dorothy Gloster, Toni Marsteller, Janice Finney, Susan Gray, Mildred Stewart, Diane DeHall; second row: John Haines Jr., Ruthann Colcombe, LaVerne Waddy, Fred Bilbrary, Dorothy Adams, Muriel Wilson, Fred DeReibertis; third row: Nick DiMomenico, Edwin Roberson, Godfrey Wills, and John E. McCormick, posed in Westinghouse High School, another version
